WEBVTT

1
00:03:22.036 --> 00:03:27.416
I have an appointment
to look at a diamond ring.

2
00:03:37.176 --> 00:03:38.636
Let me in

3
00:03:38.844 --> 00:03:41.597
or I'll take my business elsewhere.

4
00:04:06.205 --> 00:04:08.248
Open the door please!

5
00:04:44.368 --> 00:04:45.411
Hello.

6
00:11:58.635 --> 00:12:01.430
Roman. who you're always talking about?

7
00:12:06.101 --> 00:12:09.396
Lovely to meet you. Charlotte.

8
00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:11.442
Hello.

9
00:58:13.449 --> 00:58:15.492
Jewels are good.

10
00:58:15.576 --> 00:58:18.495
When he gets out. end him.

11
01:29:39.750 --> 01:29:40.918
Mummy.

12
01:33:42.284 --> 01:33:43.493
Are you OK?

13
01:33:43.952 --> 01:33:47.289
I can't wake Mummy up.

14
01:33:47.789 --> 01:33:52.377
I just want to check you're not bleeding.

15
01:33:55.714 --> 01:33:56.673
I'm OK.

16
01:33:56.757 --> 01:33:58.258
but Mummy...
